video::-webkit-media-controls {
  display:none !important;
}
.vr-controls {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 60px;
  line-height:  60px;
  display: flex;
  flex-flow: row nowrap;
  z-index: 1001;
  align-items: center;
  color: white;
  font-size: 14px;
  transition: all 1s ease-in-out;
  /* animation: mymove 1s; */
  background:linear-gradient(180deg ,rgba(0,0,0,0) 20%,rgba(0,0,0,.6) 100%);
  padding: 0 6px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  overflow: none;
  user-select: none;
}
@keyframes loading {
  from {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(1.2);
  }
  to {
    opacity: 0.1;
    transform:scale(0.6);
  }
}
.vr-loading-mask {
  position: absolute;
  z-index: 1;
  margin: 0;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}
.vr-loading-spinner {
  width: 33px;
  height: 33px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: #8385aa;
  opacity: .5;
  margin: 20px;
  color: #fff;
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 33px;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  animation: loading 0.8s infinite alternate;
}

.vr-icon-pause {
  height: 38px;
  width: 38px;
  /* margin: 0 5px; */
  background: url(data:image/png;base64,) no-repeat;
  background-size: contain;
}
.vr-icon-play {
  height: 38px;
  width: 38px;
  /* margin: 0 5px; */
  background: url(data:image/png;base64,) no-repeat;
  background-size: contain;
}
.vr-lives-pos {
  margin: 0 5px;
}
.vr-lives-pos::before {
  padding: 2px 5px;
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 12px;
  content: '\673A\4F4D';
  text-align: center;
  border: 2px solid #ffffff;
  border-radius: 5px;
}
.vr-global-error {
  position: absolute;
  z-index: 900;
  margin: 0;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}
.vr-global-error .vr-global-error-btn {
  color: #f00;
  height: 30px;
  font-size: 12px;
  line-height: 30px;
  width: 80px;
  border-radius: 15px;
  text-align: center;
  border: 1px solid #f00;
}
.vr-global-pause {
  position: absolute;
  z-index: 900;
  margin: 0;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-size: 100% 100%;
}

.vr-global-pause__contain {
  width: 50px;
  height: 50px;
  border-radius: 100%;
  border: 1px solid #fff;
  opacity: 0.7;
  background: rgba(255,255,255, 0.3);
}

.vr-global-pause__icon {
  /* margin-top: 6px;
  margin-left: 8px; */
  flex: 0 0 0;
  height: 0;
  width: 0;
  margin-top: 10px;
  margin-left: 15px;
  border-top: 14px solid transparent;
  border-bottom: 14px solid transparent;
  border-left: 27px solid #fff;
  /* border-radius: 4px;
  border-top: 8px solid transparent;
  border-bottom: 8px solid transparent;
  border-left: 14px solid #fff; */
  padding: 0;
}
@media screen and (orientation: landscape) {
  .vr-global-pause__contain {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
  }
  .vr-global-pause__icon {
    margin-top: 10px;
    margin-left: 15px;
    border-top: 14px solid transparent;
    border-bottom: 14px solid transparent;
    border-left: 27px solid #fff;
  }
}
.vr-time-current {
  height: 100%;
  line-height: 60px;
  padding: 0 4px;
  font-size: 10px;
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 120px;
  overflow: hidden;
  white-space: nowrap;
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
}
.vr-timeline-outer {
  flex: 1;
  height: 5px;
  border-radius: 3px;
  background-color: #B0B0B0;
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex;
  flex-flow: row nowrap;
  margin: 0 8px;
  position: relative;
}
.vr-timeline-inner {
  height: 100%;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(114,0,255,1) 0%,rgba(168,2,235,1) 100%);
  position: absolute;
  position: relative;
  border-radius: 3px;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
}
.vr-timeline-cached {
  height: 100%;
  background-color: #fff;
  position: absolute;
  border-radius: 3px;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
}
.vr-silder-current {
  width: 15px;
  height: 15px;
  border-radius: 100%;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(114,0,255,1) 0%,rgba(168,2,235,1) 100%);
  border: 2px solid #fff;
  transform: translate(10px, -8px);
  display: inline-block;
  box-sizing: content-box;
  position: absolute;
  right: 0;
}

/* 直播样式 */
.vr-controls[tag="live"] .vr-timeline-inner {
  width: 100%;
  background-color: #F8E71C;
}
.vr-controls[tag$="live"] .vr-timeline-outer {
  margin-right: 20px;
}
.vr-controls[tag$="live"] .vr-silder-current {
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(114,0,255,1) 0%,rgba(168,2,235,1) 100%);
  border: 2px solid #fff;
  width: 15px;
  height: 15px;
  transform: translate(12px, -8px);
}

.vr-controls[tag$="live"] .vr-rat-wrap {
  /* display: none; */
}

.vr-tran-right {
  flex: 0 0 0;
  height: 0;
  width: 0;
  border-radius: 4px;
  border-top: 10px solid transparent;
  border-bottom: 10px solid transparent;
  border-left: 20px solid #fff;
  padding: 0;
}
.vr-rat-wrap {
  margin: 0 8px;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.vr-rat-text {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 0 2px;
  color: #fff;
  height: 24px;
  line-height: 24px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  /* background-color: #1883FF; */
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: 14px;
}
.vr-rat-options {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 2rem;
  width: 100%;
}
.vr-codelist {
  position: absolute;
  width: 100px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  z-index: 1002;
  right: -22px;
  bottom: 50px;
  color: #fff;
  text-align: left;
  background-color: rgba(0, 14, 36, 0.8);
  transition:  all 0.5s;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  border-radius: 6px;
}

.vr-codelist .vr-codelist-inner {
  max-height: 200px;
  max-width: 120px;
  overflow-y: auto;
}

.vr-codelist:before,
.vr-codelist:after {
  position: absolute;
  display: block;
  width: 0;
  height: 0;
  border: solid transparent;
  pointer-events: none;
  content: "";
  border-color: transparent;
}
.vr-codelist.down:before {
  border-top-color: rgba(0, 14, 36, 0.8);
  border-width: 12px;
  left: 65%;
  margin-left: -10px;
  top: 100%;
}

.vr-rat-item {
  display: block;
  text-align: left;
  font-weight: 400;
  cursor: pointer;
  height: 30px;
  line-height: 30px;
}
.vr-rat-item + .vr-rat-item {
  margin-top: 10px;
}

.vr-voice {
  position: relative;
  width: 20px;
  height: 100%;
  cursor: pointer;
  background: url(data:image/png;base64,) no-repeat;
  background-position: center center;
  margin: 0 5px;
}
.vr-voice:hover{
  background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,);
}
.vr-voice-mute {
  background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,);
}
.vr-voice:hover .vr-voice-bar {
  display: block;
}

.vr-gyr {
  position: relative;
  width: 30px;
  height: 100%;
  cursor: pointer;
  background: url(data:image/png;base64,) no-repeat;
  background-size: contain;
  background-position: center center;
  margin: 0 5px;
}
.vr-gyr-active {
  position: relative;
  width: 30px;
  height: 100%;
  cursor: pointer;
  background: url(data:image/png;base64,) no-repeat;
  background-position: center center;
  margin: 0 5px;
  background-size: contain;
}
.vr-voice-mute:hover {
  background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,);
}
.vr-voice.vr-voice-mute:hover .vr-voice-bar {
  display: none;
}
.vr-voice-bar {
  display: none;
  position: absolute;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  height: 130px;
  width: 60px;
  padding: 15px 28px;
  background-color: rgba(2,11,25,.9);
  border-radius: 4px;
  left: -20px;
  bottom: 50px;
}
.vr-voice-bar .vr-voice-bar__slider {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  border-radius: 2px;
  background-color: #fff;
  display: flex;
  flex-flow: column nowrap;
  justify-content: flex-end;
  align-items: center;
}
.vr-voice-bar .vr-voice-bar__slider .current {
  position: relative;
  height: 10%;
  width: 100%;
  background-color: #1883FF;
}
.vr-voice-bar .vr-voice-bar__slider .current .icon {
  position: absolute;
  width: 26px;
  height: 26px;
  transform: translate(-11px, -11px);
  background: url(data:image/png;base64,);
  cursor: pointer;
}
.vr-rat-item-active {
  color: #1883FF;
}
.vr-rat-item:hover {
  color: #1883FF;
}
.vr-elem {
  margin: 0 2px;
  cursor: pointer;
  height: 100%;
  width: 42px;
  text-align: center;
  background: url(data:image/png;base64,) no-repeat center center;
  background-size: 42px 42px;
}
.vr-elem-active {
  background: url(data:image/png;base64,) no-repeat center center;
  background-size: 24px 24px;
}

.full-screen {
  margin:0 5px;
  cursor: pointer;
  height: 100%;
  width: 30px;
  text-align: center;
  background: url(data:image/png;base64,) no-repeat center center;
  background-size: 20px 20px;
}
.full-screen-exit {
  margin-right: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  height: 100%;
  width: 30px;
  background: url(data:image/png;base64,) no-repeat center center;
  background-size: 20px 20px;
}
.full-screen-active {
  position: fixed !important;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  right: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  z-index: 2000;
}
.vr-live-info {
  display: flex;
  flex-flow: row nowrap;
  justify-content: flex-start;
  align-items: center;
  margin: 0 5px;
}

.vr-videos-switch {
  margin:0 5px;
  cursor: pointer;
  height: 100%;
  width: 25px;
  text-align: center;
  background: url(data:image/png;base64,) no-repeat center center;
  background-size: 20px 20px;
}

.vr-live-text::before {
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 14px;
  content: '\76F4\64AD';
}

.vr-live-icon {
  margin-right: 6px;
  display: inline-block;
  width: 7px;
  height: 7px;
  border-radius: 100%;
  border: 1px solid #ffffff;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(114,0,255,1) 0%,rgba(168,2,235,1) 100%);;
}
